I AM BLOWN AWAY! Lets start with the complextion, it is on point. An olive tone compliments the lighting of this nature covered labirynth. The curvature of the eyes gives the model soul along with a historical past one desires to discover. Obviously the ears are the trade mark of any Elf. One can clearly see the Scapha or inner lining beneath the Helix, which is the think outline of the ear. If you look closely, you will even see the development of the Anthelix, the indension running vertically  in the center of the ear.  The Nose is spell binding as well, however, my favorite part is the Dense fibrous connective tissue, which outlines the nostrols of the nose. This is the first time i've ever seen the curature resembling a huminoid form, instead of it being flat or overly round. Next is the lips, there is so much detail the vermillon border is distinct and noticable for once. These are the two lines thats conect the bottom of your nose to your lips, it's gorgouse! You can even see the Naso-labial fold, those two lines that seperate the cheeks from the mouth. Even the roundness of the chin is amazingly detailed. The curvature of the lips is perfectly scultped to anatomy. The entire deisng ofthe face is atomically beautiful, and couldn't be an more defined. The before and after go beyond day and night, I can not wait to see what model VR perfects next!
